{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1782639609991,"sessionID":"ses_0f2671430ffeHDH7OOuiDtjCMf","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"grep","callID":"call_HVpo1T4Spju3He2Lx7B1Z0qD","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"include":"source-coverage-matrix.json","path":"D:\\workspace\\Foodike\\translation-inputs","pattern":"\"featureId\": \"app-src-main-java-com-example-foodike-presentation-home-085460c333-001-image-viewing-bitmap-exif-handling-zoom\"|\"featureId\": \"app-src-main-java-com-example-foodike-presentation-home-ec64cedf3e-003-observable-state-viewmodel-flow-livedata\"|\"status\": \"planned\"|\"status\": \"implemented\"|\"targetBehavior\":|\"verificationEvidence\":|\"factsSource\": "},"output":"Found 940 matches (showing first 100)\nD:\\workspace\\Foodike\\translation-inputs\\source-coverage-matrix.json:\n  Line 43:     \"factsSource\": [\r\n\n  Line 106:       \"targetBehavior\": \"The target content/session repositories keep this phase as pure in-memory seeded data with no file, SAF, MediaStore, or import/export path.\",\r\n\n  Line 107:       \"verificationEvidence\": [\r\n\n  Line 166:         \"factsSource\": \"agent\"\r\n\n  Line 191:       \"targetBehavior\": \"The target repositories keep media references as simple `mediaName` strings without adding viewer or bitmap-processing logic in phase-02.\",\r\n\n  Line 192:       \"verificationEvidence\": [\r\n\n  Line 253:         \"factsSource\": \"agent\"\r\n\n  Line 278:       \"targetBehavior\": \"The phase-02 content/session layer keeps seeded content separate from cross-screen state; no bundle or deeplink logic is implemented in the data source file itself.\",\r\n\n  Line 279:       \"verificationEvidence\": [\r\n\n  Line 338:         \"factsSource\": \"agent\"\r\n\n  Line 363:       \"targetBehavior\": \"The target keeps seeded content in `home_content_repository.cj` and route behavior in feature/app modules rather than mixing navigation surfaces into the data source.\",\r\n\n  Line 364:       \"verificationEvidence\": [\r\n\n  Line 423:         \"factsSource\": \"agent\"\r\n\n  Line 448:       \"targetBehavior\": \"The target keeps seeded content repositories permission-free in phase-02 and adds no request-permission scaffolding.\",\r\n\n  Line 449:       \"verificationEvidence\": [\r\n\n  Line 508:         \"factsSource\": \"agent\"\r\n\n  Line 532:       \"status\": \"planned\",\r\n\n  Line 535:       \"targetBehavior\": \"\",\r\n\n  Line 536:       \"verificationEvidence\": [],\r\n\n  Line 584:         \"factsSource\": \"agent\"\r\n\n  Line 608:       \"status\": \"planned\",\r\n\n  Line 611:       \"targetBehavior\": \"\",\r\n\n  Line 612:       \"verificationEvidence\": [],\r\n\n  Line 647:         \"factsSource\": \"template\"\r\n\n  Line 671:       \"status\": \"planned\",\r\n\n  Line 674:       \"targetBehavior\": \"\",\r\n\n  Line 675:       \"verificationEvidence\": [],\r\n\n  Line 710:         \"factsSource\": \"template\"\r\n\n  Line 734:       \"status\": \"planned\",\r\n\n  Line 737:       \"targetBehavior\": \"\",\r\n\n  Line 738:       \"verificationEvidence\": [],\r\n\n  Line 773:         \"factsSource\": \"template\"\r\n\n  Line 797:       \"status\": \"planned\",\r\n\n  Line 800:       \"targetBehavior\": \"\",\r\n\n  Line 801:       \"verificationEvidence\": [],\r\n\n  Line 836:         \"factsSource\": \"template\"\r\n\n  Line 857:       \"status\": \"implemented\",\r\n\n  Line 860:       \"targetBehavior\": \"`buildHistoryRecordCard` renders the same static order-history imagery using packaged veg/non-veg icons only.\",\r\n\n  Line 861:       \"verificationEvidence\": [\r\n\n  Line 913:         \"factsSource\": \"agent\"\r\n\n  Line 937:       \"targetBehavior\": \"`buildHistoryRecordCard` uses packaged assets only and has no protected API access.\",\r\n\n  Line 938:       \"verificationEvidence\": [\r\n\n  Line 984:         \"factsSource\": \"agent\"\r\n\n  Line 1012:       \"targetBehavior\": \"The HarmonyOS routing shell likewise keeps only route/shell behavior in this module and does not add image-viewer logic at the navigation layer.\",\r\n\n  Line 1013:       \"verificationEvidence\": [\r\n\n  Line 1059:         \"factsSource\": \"template\"\r\n\n  Line 1084:       \"status\": \"implemented\",\r\n\n  Line 1087:       \"targetBehavior\": \"`route_registry.cj`, `shell_route_state.cj`, and `FoodikeBootstrap.build()` preserve the same route inventory plus home/history-only bottom-shell and cart-action visibility semantics.\",\r\n\n  Line 1088:       \"verificationEvidence\": [\r\n\n  Line 1158:         \"factsSource\": \"agent\"\r\n\n  Line 1186:       \"targetBehavior\": \"The HarmonyOS routing shell keeps the same route/shell scope without permission prompts, and `entry/src/main/module.json5::requestPermissions` remains empty.\",\r\n\n  Line 1187:       \"verificationEvidence\": [\r\n\n  Line 1246:         \"factsSource\": \"agent\"\r\n\n  Line 1271:       \"status\": \"implemented\",\r\n\n  Line 1274:       \"targetBehavior\": \"`FoodikeBootstrap` keeps route and shell-top state in ArkUI `@State`, and `ShellRouteState` applies route commands while preserving the same visibility behavior.\",\r\n\n  Line 1275:       \"verificationEvidence\": [\r\n\n  Line 1343:         \"factsSource\": \"agent\"\r\n\n  Line 1372:       \"targetBehavior\": \"`login_page.cj` keeps the same static social sign-in icons as clickable placeholders without adding image viewer behavior.\",\r\n\n  Line 1373:       \"verificationEvidence\": [\r\n\n  Line 1429:         \"factsSource\": \"agent\"\r\n\n  Line 1455:       \"status\": \"implemented\",\r\n\n  Line 1458:       \"targetBehavior\": \"`bootstrap_page.cj` wires `renderLoginRoute` so the login button and submit action call `performLogin()`, then navigate to `home_screen` on successful credential validation.\",\r\n\n  Line 1459:       \"verificationEvidence\": [\r\n\n  Line 1520:         \"factsSource\": \"agent\"\r\n\n  Line 1549:       \"targetBehavior\": \"The Harmony login route keeps the same in-page login UI and does not add notification or widget behavior.\",\r\n\n  Line 1550:       \"verificationEvidence\": [\r\n\n  Line 1606:         \"factsSource\": \"agent\"\r\n\n  Line 1635:       \"targetBehavior\": \"The Harmony login route preserves this no-permission flow and does not introduce permission prompts.\",\r\n\n  Line 1636:       \"verificationEvidence\": [\r\n\n  Line 1694:         \"factsSource\": \"agent\"\r\n\n  Line 1720:       \"status\": \"implemented\",\r\n\n  Line 1723:       \"targetBehavior\": \"`FoodikeBootstrap` owns the login route state and keeps the login inputs/error message in route state while the login page is active; no extra resume/pause refresh path exists in the source flow.\",\r\n\n  Line 1724:       \"verificationEvidence\": [\r\n\n  Line 1785:         \"factsSource\": \"agent\"\r\n\n  Line 1814:       \"targetBehavior\": \"The Harmony login route keeps this non-configurable login surface and does not invent settings toggles.\",\r\n\n  Line 1815:       \"verificationEvidence\": [\r\n\n  Line 1871:         \"factsSource\": \"agent\"\r\n\n  Line 1897:       \"status\": \"implemented\",\r\n\n  Line 1900:       \"targetBehavior\": \"`FoodikeBootstrap` owns `loginEmail`, `loginPassword`, and `loginErrorMessage` state and passes change handlers into `renderLoginRoute`, so text input and error feedback update immediately while the route is active.\",\r\n\n  Line 1901:       \"verificationEvidence\": [\r\n\n  Line 1964:         \"factsSource\": \"agent\"\r\n\n  Line 1990:       \"status\": \"implemented\",\r\n\n  Line 1993:       \"targetBehavior\": \"`login_store.cj` preserves the same hard-coded credentials and `bootstrap_page.cj::performLogin` preserves the same success/failure split by toggling persisted login state on success and showing an immediate error message plus toast on failure.\",\r\n\n  Line 1994:       \"verificationEvidence\": [\r\n\n  Line 2058:         \"factsSource\": \"agent\"\r\n\n  Line 2081:       \"status\": \"planned\",\r\n\n  Line 2084:       \"targetBehavior\": \"\",\r\n\n  Line 2085:       \"verificationEvidence\": [],\r\n\n  Line 2120:         \"factsSource\": \"template\"\r\n\n  Line 2143:       \"status\": \"planned\",\r\n\n  Line 2146:       \"targetBehavior\": \"\",\r\n\n  Line 2147:       \"verificationEvidence\": [],\r\n\n  Line 2182:         \"factsSource\": \"template\"\r\n\n  Line 2205:       \"status\": \"planned\",\r\n\n  Line 2208:       \"targetBehavior\": \"\",\r\n\n  Line 2209:       \"verificationEvidence\": [],\r\n\n  Line 2244:         \"factsSource\": \"template\"\r\n\n  Line 2267:       \"status\": \"planned\",\r\n\n  Line 2270:       \"targetBehavior\": \"\",\r\n\n  Line 2271:       \"verificationEvidence\": [],\r\n\n\n(Results truncated: showing 100 of 940 matches (840 hidden). Consider using a more specific path or pattern.)","metadata":{"matches":940,"truncated":true},"title":"\"featureId\": \"app-src-main-java-com-example-foodike-presentation-home-085460c333-001-image-viewing-bitmap-exif-handling-zoom\"|\"featureId\": \"app-src-main-java-com-example-foodike-presentation-home-ec64cedf3e-003-observable-state-viewmodel-flow-livedata\"|\"status\": \"planned\"|\"status\": \"implemented\"|\"targetBehavior\":|\"verificationEvidence\":|\"factsSource\": ","time":{"start":1782639609829,"end":1782639609989}},"id":"prt_f0d99c78b0010hgylhvW8GprDh","sessionID":"ses_0f2671430ffeHDH7OOuiDtjCMf","messageID":"msg_f0d9998ab001apfeirfLBNtwTy"}}
